pageContext.claim: “How did they let that happen?" And how come it didn't go into other sections of China? Why did they block it from leaving Wuhan but they didn't block it from going to the rest of the world, including the United States? Why is that? Beijing doesn't have it; other places don't have it.”
pageContext.analysis: There were cases of covid-19 in Beijing as well as several other parts of China.
